{"tid":2097154,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★長實 趙國雄：納米樓一定會爆煲 唔好掂，二手都冇人買！","createTime":"2020-07-06T14:58:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T11:34:46.000Z","uid":19454,"like":147,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"1868afa7d9993397b6cbdb04e04e66f45fae8a4a","tid":2097154,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T14:58:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呼籲市民「一定唔好掂」納米樓<br />\n</span><br />\n長實執行董事趙國雄於《香港01》財經節目「財經加零一」中表示，納米樓面積太細，參考外國的納米單位，「外國只係畀人返工（居住）用，假日已經返去自己主要居所」。他坦言個人最反對納米樓，相信納米樓「供應到一定程度一定飽和，之後就冇人再會接受，我自己都預期遲早一定會爆煲，我當時都呼籲市民一定唔好掂，唔好張資金綁住係個度，二手都冇人買」。因此認為，無論以投資或自用的角度來說，都不應購買。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/494320/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%8A%A0%E9%9B%B6%E4%B8%80-%E8%B6%B3%E6%9C%AC%E9%87%8D%E6%BA%AB-%E9%95%B7%E5%AF%A6-%E6%A8%93%E7%A5%9E-%E8%B6%99%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%84%E9%A0%90%E8%AD%A6-%E7%B4%8D%E7%B1%B3%E6%A8%93%E9%81%B2%E6%97%A9%E7%88%86%E7%85%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A%2F494320%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%258A%25A0%25E9%259B%25B6%25E4%25B8%2580-%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E6%259C%25AC%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%25BA%25AB-%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%25AF%25A6-%25E6%25A8%2593%25E7%25A5%259E-%25E8%25B6%2599%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259B%2584%25E9%25A0%2590%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E7%25B4%258D%25E7%25B1%25B3%25E6%25A8%2593%25E9%2581%25B2%25E6%2597%25A9%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%2585%25B2&d=uYDAXyhVPN7xTSuHIXBXEvzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=a620a0c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/494320/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%8A%A0%E9%9B%B6%E4%B8%80-%E8%B6%B3%E6%9C%AC%E9%87%8D%E6%BA%AB-%E9%95%B7%E5%AF%A6-%E6%A8%93%E7%A5%9E-%E8%B6%99%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%84%E9%A0%90%E8%AD%A6-%E7%B4%8D%E7%B1%B3%E6%A8%93%E9%81%B2%E6%97%A9%E7%88%86%E7%85%B2</a>"},{"pid":"27e155dd78e2abd6fefb0576316c3efb43c02e96","tid":2097154,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,